        We audit your current AI citation baseline, map your query architecture gaps, and deliver a prioritised AEO strategy with clear 90-day milestones. The audit is a standalone deliverable — no retainer required to start.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
